    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "1 [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "(Nationalities Intelligence)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "By letter 12/7/58 Mr. [REDACTED] inquired whether we",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "could furnish him any information concerning the [REDACTED] and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "advised he was asking the Bureau since he had recently learned that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "FBI is involved in this affair. [REDACTED] explained that [REDACTED] formed the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED] in Bridgeport, Connecticut, in 1952",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "to look into the flying saucer mystery. In 1953 [REDACTED] allegedly stated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "that he knew what the saucers are. Then according to [REDACTED] \"three men",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "in black suits\" silenced [REDACTED] to the extent that even today [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "will not discuss the matter of his \"hush-up\" with anyone. [REDACTED] pointed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "out he has learned that \"the secret of the saucers lies the 'dreadful",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "underground menace' that is threatening the world\" and that he has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "important information concerning this menace. [REDACTED] also requested our",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "help in getting in touch with [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Bufiles contain no information on [REDACTED] The only identifiable",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "data in our files on [REDACTED] is a letter he wrote on 10/26/52 on the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "letterhead of the [REDACTED] to a Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Franklin, Indiana, in which he suggested how [REDACTED] could organize",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "a chapter of the Saucer Bureau in Franklin. Also in Bufiles is a copy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "of the January, 1953, magazine \"Space Review\" which apparently was put",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "out by the Saucer Bureau. This magazine contains numerous articles and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "squibs concerning the sighting of flying saucers throughout the world.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "It does not appear to have any security significance.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "RECOMMENDATION:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "There is a possibility that [REDACTED] may be suffering from de-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "lusions; however, in view of the fact that he stated the FBI is involved",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "in a matter of which we are not cognizant as well as the implications in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "his description of the \"hush-up\" of [REDACTED], it is recommended he be inter-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "viewed and all information in his possession concerning this incident be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "obtained so that we can decide whether the facts warrant investigation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "At the same time his letter will be orally acknowledged.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "A letter to Phoenix is enclosed. REC-37 62-93971-378",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
